Endpoint of semi-major axis (Vertex)=(-3,3) -> semi-major axis a = |3 - 1| = 2 ->
Ellipse relation b^2 = a^2 - c^2 -> b^2 = 2^2 - 1^2 = 3 ->
Semi-minor axis b = \sqrt{3}

